1b1efb97efa0","tid":1465730,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"用衫連耳仔都遮埋（遮耳機）果兩個，係咁鬧記者係咁鬧 first aid!!!!!!!!!!! 頭先引人出去追警車！ 仲用鐵馬扔警車！ <br />\n<br />\n捉佢兩個！ diu <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6563fbc07b81ca86a096e22d5944bcd7eeea25","tid":1465730,"uid":295648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到自己個po<br />\n<br />\n公安單野<br />\n<br />\n親身同現場個外國記者傾過<br />\n求認真睇<br />\n<br />\n中後段我先到場<br />\n發現有3個可疑人喺到唱雙簧<br />\n不段話見到踢人打人既係帶住耳機，叫我地放人<br />\n佢地不停轉換位置，然後相繼認同對方<br />\n<br />\n跟住我見到有外國記者解釋經過<br />\n佢係第一身見到事發經過，有show相比我地睇<br />\n首先佢話個疑似公安一被發現<br />\n已經好多人圍上去想出手<br />\n佢影到一個人攞住棍想打<br />\n上前想保個公安，比人打傷埋<br />\n個個不斷踢，個記者用身去擋都踢<br />\n眼同手都受傷，比人拉返出來先無事<br />\n佢話開頭用棍篤人嗰個一打完就散水<br />\n我問有無見到&rdquo;帶耳機人&rdquo;<br />\n佢話無，但太亂不能肯定<br />\n<br />\n比人完美劇本哂啦！<br />\n機場張皇牌送出去比人！"},{"pid":"6162e3cb5f9093ec12e711f6e1332779568a4a60","tid":1465730,"uid":302057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae6566e3b22332b6ba6fae2a9e631cbcf3daf266","tid":1465730,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"推 +1包實全面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"好大機會鬼 一網打盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa865c6b327b41896f7fc0beaff04e4a914c670","tid":1465730,"uid":201384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1068d6fae4a63d8e3e79b08146e9a3ebf5324887","tid":1465730,"uid":87828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>散左之後<br />\n唔該搵人扯開個幾個激動包撚實晒既人<br />\n好撚大機會係鬼</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KU7LvTC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKU7LvTC.png&h=fd1f80b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/003202_562670ddbc42ff918a7e860e765cce79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F003202_562670ddbc42ff918a7e860e765cce79.png&h=536e72a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/003205_720f03fd760d28ac9d71327e9c6f4465.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F003205_720f03fd760d28ac9d71327e9c6f4465.png&h=0e833e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金毛一開頭係人群中搞事，後尾警察黎到俾自己人（應該係警察）帶走了"},{"pid":"f0c2431a8d2ef2032901801173b50639cfa550d8","tid":1465730,"uid":267312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c64250ddd62e9de12bba9f07f69c632c08c8c31","tid":1465730,"uid":289686,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"反正無退路，都唔係咩都做就會羸<br />\n捉棋都唔係只睇一步<br />\n<br />\n我依家唔係前線，頭先走左，唔知情況，不過我地係有機會贏，唔係咩都衝就贏，如果唔係攬巴搞個國際文宣做咩？ 兩個幾鐘眾籌 千五萬有多你估少人？<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，都要大家互相睇下大家做緊咩，至少唔會抵銷其他手足做緊既野<br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫停任何野，只係出post, 保持下理性，不喜隨便屌<br />\n不割<br />\n<br />\n不過我既目標係 五大訴求"},{"pid":"84f6e6eefaa694a825f360532353c5d1e880fa65","tid":1465730,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"推 嗰幾件唔撚抵幫"},{"pid":"946b507607c6c59aab1d4c8c469a6959fc92bf71","tid":1465730,"uid":262113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f7922d0b683eda5c8262c46be24b45d1a18b4d2","tid":1465730,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"好大機會古惑仔黎"},{"pid":"c12c3176c05c73c4f44c7466ac5f1fcaffc996dc","tid":1465730,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"又捉咩鬼呀"},{"pid":"8d9091ca203c995d73d91b4d1292f1d711181863","tid":1465730,"uid":304860,"like":0,"dislike":